SECTION 4 — ENABLE AI SYSTEM QUESTIONS

The Workflow Agent AiBox should be able to answer system-level questions.

Examples:

Which workflows fail most often?
Which workflow takes the longest to complete?
Which step causes the most delays?
What should I optimize first?

The AI must analyze:

workflow runs  
failures  
approval delays  
step execution time

and respond with structured insights.

